data.description: UNDER MARKET VALUE! Discover this desirable SW Cape Coral living in this exquisite POOL home. Boasting a thoughtfully designed split floor plan that encompasses 3 generously sized bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and the convenience of an attached 2 garage. NEW UPGRADES are aplenty, featuring a pristine BRAND NEW ROOF, HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS for enhanced security, and a fully fenced yard. Step outside and embrace the ultimate Florida lifestyle – soak in the glorious southern exposure while lounging on your stylish paver deck, and savor the tranquility of your private pool area, offering abundant space for all your entertainment needs. The appeal of this home extends beyond its walls; its prime location provides effortless access to dining and shopping, elevating your daily living experience. This gem is NOT in a flood zone! Offered at an unbeatable price, this home presents unparalleled value in this highly sought-after area. Don't let this golden opportunity slip through your fingers – act now to schedule your showing before someone else seizes this incredible deal.
